Mba firy amintsika izao manora-tena ho mpivavaka
Mba firy amintsika izao no efa tena vonon-kibebaka
Sao kosa dia fahazarana sy fisehoana hiavaka
Ka tonga ho henatra ho an’iTompo Andriamanintsika e!


Mangataka Pardon
Mangataka Pardon amin’ny zanakao Andriamanitro ô!
Mangataka Pardon e!
Mpanompo tsy mahasoa izahay, ka dia mangata-pifonanae!


Isan’andro tsy mahafoy ny rendrarendran’ny tany
Ny vola no himatesana sy tompoina amin’izany
Andevozinny fahantrana fa tsy mahita mangirana
Ka indro fa milomay, mankany amin’ny fahotana e!


Tonga nidina tety, Ilay Tompo be fitia
Tonga mba hamonjy antsika, noho ireo ota tsy hita isa
Nefa dia nampahoriana, niaritra ny fijaliana
Ho avotra ho ahy sy ianao, amin’izao tontolo izao